description: Apparently originating from an analogy between the distention of the arm muscles and the distended belly of a python that has swallowed a large animal.

entries.meaning: (bodybuilding, slang) Large and well-developed muscles in the upper arm.
examples: I read in another magazine about a workout that can put a whole inch on your arms in just one day! Obviously that sounds awesome, because my guns are only 15 inches. I figure I could do this workout every couple months and within a year, I will have the big 20-inch pythons!
